    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a rather rare species of the weasel family that is dark in color, agile in trees, has a slender body, pursues prey into hollow trees or burrows, and despite its name rarely eats fish.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
